ZH: 他吞咽下一口热腾腾的鸡汤。
EN: He swallowed a sip of hot chicken soup.

ZH: 在感冒期间，你应该避免吞咽含糖片剂。
EN: During a cold, you should avoid swallowing lozenges.

ZH: 那块肉太大了，我无法一口吞咽。
EN: That piece of meat is too big to swallow in one bite.

ZH: 她哽咽着说出了她的不幸遭遇。
EN: She choked and spoke out about her unfortunate experience.

ZH: 我强忍住眼泪，吞咽下失望的事实。
EN: I swallowed the disappointing fact, holding back my tears.

ZH: 他吞咽了一些维生素片来提高免疫力。
EN: He swallowed some vitamin pills to boost his immune system.

